965046077797.summary: Welcome to the Digital Ministry Conference 2025 ! Join us at the Gaylord Texan Resort & Convention Center for a pre NRB event filled with inspiring talks, interactive workshops, and networking opportunities. Whether you're a seasoned digital ministry pro or just starting out, this event is perfect for anyone looking to learn and grow in the world of online ministry. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to connect with like-minded individuals and gain valuable insights to take your digital ministry to the next level. See you there! For more information visit digitialministryconference.com
